    <text>
        <body>
        	<div1 type="letter">
        		<head>Edwin A. Alderman to Mrs. Sarah R. McConnell <date value="1917-03-28">March 28, 1917.</date></head>
           
            <opener>
            <dateline>
            <name type="place">University of Virginia<lb/>
            Charlottesville<lb/>
            Office of the President.</name><lb/>
            <date value="1917-03-28">March 28, 1917.</date><lb/>
            <lb/>
            Mrs. Sarah R. McConnell,<lb/>
            Seabreeze, Fla.<lb/>
            </dateline><lb/>
            
            <salute>My dear Mrs. McConnell:</salute>
            </opener>
        		
            <p>
            The faculty and students of the University of
            Virginia share with you your great sorrow in the loss of your son
            and what must be your noble pride in his splendid valor and heroic
            death.  At a meeting of our faculty last night, I told the story of
            his life to them.  It is the desire of the faculty, students, and
            friends of James McConnell to place a memorial here to him, which
            shall, in enduring forms of beauty, express to future generations
            the meaning of idealism, valor, and devotion to freedom and right.
            This University has lived one hundred years.  Its sons have borne
            a big part in every great national crisis.  No single one of them
            has met death with more courage and nobler self-sacrifice than
            your son, and you have a right, therefore, to taste the sweetness
            of the noblest pride in his achievement while struggling with the
            grief that a mother must have for the loss of her son.  This <reg orig="Univer-|sity">University</reg>
            shares that pride and that grief in fullest measure.
            </p>
        		
        		<closer>
            <salute>Faithfully yours,</salute>
            
            <signed>Edwin A. Alderman,</signed>
            
            President.
            </closer>
            
            <!-- File: McConnell/ Alderman -->
            
            </div1>
